{"title": "Bring Him to Me", "content": "I will not interrogate my enemies in the inner sanctum \u2014 a small hotel well outside my borders will work just as well.\n\nA Big Bad brings the captured heroes to his/her lair \u2014 and frequently the very heart of it. For bonus points, sending all the guards away so he can talk to the hero in private.\n\nYeah, this is always a smart idea. Bring your enemy deep into the control center of your base, and dismiss the guards. There's no way he can mess things up from there...\n\nAny simpler solution seems to be out of the question, after all, for some reason, the Big Bad wants them alive.\n\nCompare Kneel Before Zod. When the heroes want or otherwise allow this, it's Captured on Purpose.\n\nNot to be confused with Bathe Her and Bring Her to Me. Except when it is.", "url": "https://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BringHimToMe", "media_links": ["/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Manga/GaRei", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Manga/Bleach", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Anime/MobileSuitGundamAge", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Manga/ApocalypseNoToride", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/ABCWarriors", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/UltimateSpiderMan", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Anime/SailorMoon", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Franchise/StarWars", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Film/ANewHope", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Film/TheEmpireStrikesBack", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Film/ReturnOfTheJedi", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Film/TheForceAwakens", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Film/JamesBond", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Film/Goldfinger", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Film/YouOnlyLiveTwice", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Film/DiamondsAreForever", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Film/TheSpyWhoLovedMe", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Film/Moonraker", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Film/GoldenEye", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Film/StarTrekFirstContact", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Film/CaptainAmericaTheFirstAvenger", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Franchise/StarWarsLegends", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/KnightsOfTheOldRepublic", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/XWingSeries", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/DarkEmpire", "/pmwiki/pm